    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>/authors/admin/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/authors/admin/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I am a Full-Time Teaching Professor at the &lt;a href=&#34;https://tec.mx/en/innovation-and-transformation/bs-in-industrial-engineering&#34;&gt;Department of Industrial Engineering&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=&#34;https://tec.mx/en&#34;&gt;Tecnológico de Monterrey&lt;/a&gt;. Previously, I was an Assistant Professor at the &lt;a href=&#34;https://industrial-engineering.uark.edu/&#34;&gt;Department of Industrial Engineering&lt;/a&gt; at the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.uark.edu/&#34;&gt;University of Arkansas&lt;/a&gt;. From 2020 to 2022, I was an Assistant Adjunct Professor at the &lt;a href=&#34;http://statistics.ucla.edu/&#34;&gt;Department of Statistics&lt;/a&gt; at the &lt;a href=&#34;https://ucla.edu/&#34;&gt;University of California, Los Angeles (UCLA)&lt;/a&gt;, and a Junior Postdoctoral Fellow of the Research Foundation Flanders (&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.fwo.be/en/&#34;&gt;FWO&lt;/a&gt;), Belgium. From July 2018 to September 2019, I was a Postdoctoral Researcher at the Department of Biosystems at &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.biw.kuleuven.be/biosyst/english&#34;&gt;KU Leuven&lt;/a&gt;, Belgium. In May 2018, I obtained a Ph.D. in Applied Economics at the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.uantwerpen.be/en/about-uantwerp/faculties/faculty-of-business-and-economics/&#34;&gt;University of Antwerp&lt;/a&gt;, Belgium. The supervisors of my Ph.D. thesis were Prof. &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.experimental-design.eu/who/&#34;&gt;Peter Goos&lt;/a&gt; and Dr. &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.experimental-design.eu/who/&#34;&gt;Eric Schoen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I was born and raised in Monterrey, Nuevo Leon, Mexico.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
